longBusinessSummary: Sino-Life Group Limited, an investment holding company, provides funeral services in the People's Republic of China, Taiwan, Hong Kong, and Vietnam. It operates through the segments Funeral Services; and Stem Cells and Immunocytes and Other Business. The company offers funeral arrangement services to funeral and non-funeral services deed holders; and cremation and cemetery services in funeral parlours and funeral service centers. It also sells burial plots and tombstones; and provides cemetery maintenance services, as well as elderly care and related consultancy services. In addition, the company provides advisory service on stem cells and immunocytes; and sells biotechnical machinery. Sino-Life Group Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Sheung Wan, Hong Kong.
